Code.Geometry
Class Line

java.lang.Object
  Code.Geometry.Line

public class Line
extends java.lang.Object

there are two parameters used for straight line. one is slope and the other one is constant parameter. This is from basic straight line equation y = mx + c where m is slope, c is constant. for vertical lines the equation is x = c and slope is positive infinite.
